@startuml
title Network management between a terminal and its host (canm)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #DEEEF0
  BorderColor #1F7A8C
}
skinparam ArrowColor #1F7A8C
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #DEEEF0
skinparam noteBorderColor #1F7A8C

[Terminal / acceptor] as T
[Acquirer host] as H

T --> H : canm.001 Network Management Initiation\n(sign-on, echo test)
H --> T : canm.002 Network Management Response
T --> H : canm.003 Key Exchange Initiation
H --> T : canm.004 Key Exchange Response
note bottom of H : keeps the session up and the\ncryptographic keys current for cain traffic
@enduml
